---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Markdown from '../components/Markdown.astro';

const explainer = `
**AmicBridge connects private lenders and private borrowers — safely and simply.**

We do not hold money, approve loans, or guarantee agreements.  
AmicBridge is a meeting place where people can find each other, talk, and make private arrangements on their own terms.

### How It Works
1. Create a profile as a lender or borrower.  
2. Post what you’re offering or looking for.  
3. Use our messaging system to connect privately.

Everything about money happens *outside* our platform — we are only the bridge between people.

### What You Can Do Here
- Create a verified profile.  
- Post borrower requests or lender offers.  
- Communicate privately and securely.  
- Build trust with ratings and reviews.  
- Follow clear safety guidelines to stay protected.

AmicBridge is about **connection**, not control.  
You stay in charge of your agreements — we simply help you meet the right people.
`;
---

<Layout title="Welcome to AmicBridge">

  <!-- Main Title -->
  <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-8">Welcome to AmicBridge</h1>

  <!-- Markdown Content -->
  <Markdown content={explainer} class="mb-12 text-lg leading-relaxed" />

  <!-- Create Profile Button -->
  <a 
    href="https://wa.me/4792928373?text=Hi%2C+I+want+to+create+a+profile+on+AmicBridge"
    target="_blank"
    class="bg-blue-400 hover:bg-blue-500 text-slate-900 font-semibold px-10 py-3 rounded-lg block text-center shadow-lg mb-10 w-max"
  >
    Create My Profile
  </a>

  <!-- Action Buttons -->
  <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-6 mt-10">

    <!-- Loan Button -->
    <a 
      href="https://wa.me/4792928373?text=Hi%2C+I+need+a+loan+from+AmicBridge"
      target="_blank"
      class="bg-rose-400 hover:bg-rose-500 text-slate-900 font-semibold px-12 py-4 rounded-lg block text-center shadow-lg"
    >
      I Need a Loan
    </a>

    <!-- Lend Button -->
    <a 
      href="https://wa.me/4792928373?text=Hi%2C+I+want+to+lend+money+through+AmicBridge"
      target="_blank"
      class="bg-rose-400 hover:bg-rose-500 text-slate-900 font-semibold px-12 py-4 rounded-lg block text-center shadow-lg"
    >
      I Want to Lend
    </a>

  </div>

  <!-- Pricing & Unlock Info -->
  <section class="mt-16 max-w-2xl space-y-4">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Payment for unlocking contact</h2>

    <p class="text-slate-300">
      AmicBridge does not charge any fee on the loan itself. Instead, we charge a small fee
      when you want to unlock the contact details of a lender or borrower that matches you.
    </p>

    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-slate-300 space-y-1">
      <li>You first contact us on WhatsApp and tell us what you need.</li>
      <li>We look for a suitable lender or borrower in our network.</li>
      <li>When you want their direct contact details, you pay a one-time unlock fee.</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="text-slate-300">
      Current unlock fee: <strong>500 NOK per contact</strong>.
    </p>

    <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">
      Payment is handled directly with AmicBridge (for example via whatsappto <strong>92928373</strong>).
      After payment is confirmed, we send you the contact details of the lender or borrower.
      All loan agreements and money transfers still happen privately between you and the other person.
    </p>
  </section>

</Layout>
